SYNOPSIS
      xed <filename|macro>

DESCRIPTION
      Frontend for ed giving you the possibility to use the xtool macros
      for the filename. 

NOTES
      If you give a filename, and the filename+".c" exists, the last will
      be used. To edit plain filename, you need to use ed.

EXAMPLE
      xed $h
      xed /d/orient/common/npc/monk
      xed $m.2